arguments.prompt: The prompt which will be used to generate images
arguments.neg_prompt: What don't you want to see in images
arguments.steps: In how many steps will be images generated
arguments.seed: What seed will be used to generate images; same seed gives same images
arguments.cfg_scale: How much model will be guided by your prompt, default is 7
arguments.res_x: Width of generated images in pixels
arguments.res_y: Height of images generated in pixels
arguments.sampler: Method (sampler) which will be used to generate images

ping.command: If the bot doesn't say it is alive... well, RIP Bot

list.command: See all available options of corresponding item

messages.cancel_dismiss: Only who created this job can cancel it
